Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.68,0:04:03.92,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(720,230)\frz19}壓\N歲\N錢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.96,0:04:09.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慶賀新年
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:11.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.65,0:04:13.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是二宮同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.49,0:04:16.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新年快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.19,0:04:18.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年會鼓動起幹勁加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.71,0:04:19.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.87,0:04:21.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請快點進行表演吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:24.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我拿起這把傘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.52,0:04:27.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用它把二宮同學轉起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.81,0:04:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將被轉起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.05,0:04:31.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.45,0:04:31.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:33.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二宮同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.91,0:04:34.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:35.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二宮同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.32,0:04:36.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:37.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內田要幾個年糕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.05,0:04:39.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.52,0:04:47.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了新年參拜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.19,0:04:49.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿了壓歲錢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.01,0:04:52.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放了風箏轉了陀螺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.25,0:04:55.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可內田還是依然每天來我家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的年糕湯你吃了兩塊年糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.32,0:05:02.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個一組是常識啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.41,0:05:05.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二貫壽司放一碟也是同樣的道理
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.46,0:05:06.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回轉壽司啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.21,0:05:10.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內田  你知道貫這個單位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:15.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內田在別人家裡吃了一堆年糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.36,0:05:21.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內田把紅豆湯都喝得一乾二淨了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.24,0:05:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就是睡覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.83,0:05:34.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是夏天拍的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:36.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去海邊的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.17,0:05:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.89,0:05:40.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.87,0:05:43.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後這個是夏天時內田的肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.10,0:05:47.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在會變成怎麼樣的慘狀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:51.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太…太誇張了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:54.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  那明天去溫水泳池吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.57,0:05:58.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果年末年初沒有過著慵懶的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.84,0:06:00.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不會有問題的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.62,0:06:08.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然來泳池  到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.39,0:06:10.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈突然要來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.89,0:06:13.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈總是很突然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.75,0:06:18.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  趁這個機會為了夏天來練習游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:20.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野  來幫我下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:21.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:22.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.01,0:06:26.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊  夏奈  放手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:27.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  這個肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.19,0:06:29.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.88,0:06:32.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是年糕太好吃的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.11,0:06:34.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看  怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.23,0:06:35.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成什麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.67,0:06:39.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  還可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.19,0:06:40.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.41,0:06:44.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經當不了新娘了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.40,0:06:45.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.75,0:06:49.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得來到泳池卻沒什麼可以做的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.98,0:06:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的只是為了這個才來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.90,0:06:54.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來還想弄個特訓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.41,0:06:58.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓內田那不像樣的肚子瘦下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.86,0:07:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  特訓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.78,0:07:02.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  內田
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:04.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那肚子是何等不堪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:08.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  又不是那麼嚴重的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.45,0:07:10.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須趁現在縮回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.13,0:07:15.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  要採取地獄溫水減肥特訓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.28,0:07:17.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.77,0:07:19.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像有了幹勁的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.26,0:07:21.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我考慮了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:24.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然接受過游泳的特訓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:26.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我還沒有特訓過別人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想特訓別人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.04,0:07:29.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.68,0:07:33.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後就叫我魔鬼教官
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.77,0:07:35.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算叫你魔鬼教官…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:37.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內田  還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.32,0:07:40.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年的泳池教學中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.68,0:07:44.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不要放手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.38,0:07:45.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.71,0:07:47.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.23,0:07:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怨你的一不留神  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.50,0:07:57.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.90,0:07:59.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.25,0:08:00.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以來特訓啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.14,0:08:03.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是復仇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.15,0:08:05.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,披著特訓皮的復仇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.49,0:08:08.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野  救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.23,0:08:11.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  魔鬼教官
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.83,0:08:14.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午飯之後再特訓怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.82,0:08:15.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.94,0:08:19.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來這裡的食堂做出來的東西似乎很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.58,0:08:20.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香這樣說的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.95,0:08:23.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霜淇淋也很好吃啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.61,0:08:26.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬天的霜淇淋是最棒的享受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.24,0:08:32.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  去吃午飯吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.38,0:08:33.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.47,0:08:39.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:41.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.57,0:08:43.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧春香的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:44.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.66,0:08:46.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那下回把圭子她們也叫來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:48.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天為什麼沒有叫她們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.68,0:08:50.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家不是去旅行就是回老家去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.08,0:08:53.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.23,0:08:55.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想去旅行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.48,0:08:56.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再去一次嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.42,0:08:58.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩天一夜的南家旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.79,0:09:00.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下…下回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.59,0:09:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.92,0:09:08.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的肚子才是最需要特訓的啊  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.49,0:09:09.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰是千秋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.71,0:09:11.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我魔鬼教官
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.44,0:09:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼既然肚子也飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.52,0:09:16.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔鬼教官  先睡一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.97,0:09:19.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔鬼教官盡情享受慵懶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.55,0:09:28.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:30.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.42,0:09:33.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別大喲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.38,0:09:34.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼大的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.28,0:09:37.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是覺得比想像中的小一些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.98,0:09:39.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是特別的漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.17,0:09:43.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊兩個人在寒假的時候去海外旅行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.09,0:09:48.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像去看了什麼有名的建築
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:51.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊  我也想去海外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.60,0:09:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利子寒假的時候去了哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.27,0:10:00.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就去了奶奶家那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶家似乎很遠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.21,0:10:04.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.73,0:10:06.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京都相當遠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.10,0:10:07.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.07,0:10:08.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是京都啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.03,0:10:09.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.76,0:10:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說  夏奈  特別大的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.74,0:10:13.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.94,0:10:16.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個建築叫什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.31,0:10:19.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:20.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.34,0:10:23.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美雪你究竟去了哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.81,0:10:26.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.21,0:10:28.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.45,0:10:31.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭子呢  去了哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.35,0:10:36.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？喂  圭子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.01,0:10:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.81,0:10:39.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我在發呆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.71,0:10:40.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在考慮什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.20,0:10:43.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  三學期開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.71,0:10:45.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就是馬拉松大會了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.91,0:10:47.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想到這個就鬱悶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.95,0:10:51.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  馬拉松大會要跑多遠來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.79,0:10:53.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想是6英里左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.79,0:10:57.19,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}1英里＝1.6千米
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.87,0:10:57.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  我以為是26英里左右呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.32,0:10:59.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要說英里？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.35,0:11:01.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過趁現在開始訓練就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.90,0:11:04.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看春天還有體檢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.27,0:11:06.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始減肥的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.27,0:11:07.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也…也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.86,0:11:10.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒假的時候重了4磅左右
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.86,0:11:12.44,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}1磅約＝453.6克
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.71,0:11:12.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不注意的話就會超過100磅…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.46,0:11:14.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說為什麼是磅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.33,0:11:16.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不明白什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.26,0:11:18.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說千米千克之類的不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.16,0:11:21.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.57,0:11:24.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是維持著海外心情可不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.17,0:11:26.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是海外心情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.77,0:11:28.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利子  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.56,0:11:29.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.93,0:11:31.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.47,0:11:32.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.11,0:11:34.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  海外組的兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.81,0:11:39.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利子的京都心情還沒有散去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.46,0:11:41.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本人注意到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.49,0:11:42.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.02,0:11:44.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利子和往常一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.87,0:11:45.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.65,0:11:47.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.84,0:11:50.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有馬拉松和體檢真是鬱悶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.78,0:11:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,0:11:52.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被傳染了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.89,0:11:55.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了  事到如今
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.37,0:11:58.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  南同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.23,0:12:02.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫幫我藤岡  大家都去京都了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.58,0:12:04.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京都？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.71,0:12:06.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬拉松是要跑多少公里來著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:08.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想應該是10公里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.30,0:12:13.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  我還以為是42.195公里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:14.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是全長馬拉松啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.16,0:12:17.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩步調好一致啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.43,0:12:20.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此  跑馬拉松又能讓人瘦多少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.66,0:12:23.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是每日堅持就不會瘦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.49,0:12:27.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是跑10公里體重就能減2公斤就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.55,0:12:28.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.37,0:12:30.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在說馬拉松大賽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.37,0:12:32.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.57,0:12:34.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的  因為就快要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.07,0:12:37.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.50,0:12:39.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡同學的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.46,0:12:43.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  藤岡同學你是不是有點曬黑了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.16,0:12:44.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放假時有去哪裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.01,0:12:46.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？能看的出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.45,0:12:48.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前被帶著去單板滑雪了  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.25,0:12:49.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點被雪反射的太陽光曬黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.69,0:12:51.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.99,0:12:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曬痕像鬍子一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.65,0:12:54.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很會滑雪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.78,0:12:55.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好啦  也就還行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.23,0:13:01.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  大家都從京都回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.83,0:13:03.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼回來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.74,0:13:07.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是回來了  剛才有一瞬間變回了正常的腔調
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.27,0:13:08.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈說話好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.06,0:13:10.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  算了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.99,0:13:12.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,200)}南家鬥惡龍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.99,0:13:12.05,title1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,500)}終於要對決了！！魔王篇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.00,0:13:17.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,200)}南家鬥惡龍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.00,0:13:17.03,title1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,500)}危險！勇者篇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.05,0:13:27.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是火鍋好啊  吃火鍋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.18,0:13:29.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火鍋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:32.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為冷就提議吃火鍋也太不動腦子了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.86,0:13:34.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再好好想想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:36.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯那就吃火鍋吧  做起來還方便
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.84,0:13:39.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是要吃火鍋啊  春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.24,0:13:41.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種大冷天吃火鍋最好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.64,0:13:42.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.32,0:13:47.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石頭剪刀布
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.92,0:13:52.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有客人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.64,0:13:56.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  春香  一起去外面玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.09,0:13:58.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下大雪了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:14:00.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去打雪仗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.57,0:14:05.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  你們不知道積雪了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:07.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.37,0:14:10.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為知道才在被爐裡懶洋洋的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.25,0:14:15.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就先從被爐裡出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.35,0:14:19.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  別看我這樣  我也是很怕冷的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.57,0:14:20.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看我這樣  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.10,0:14:24.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從被爐爬出來是需要事先做心理準備的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.62,0:14:26.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.38,0:14:28.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香在寫什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.97,0:14:30.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.31,0:14:32.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  夏奈  這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.05,0:14:33.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:37.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出門的話就拜託你順便買點東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.33,0:14:42.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來春香是肯定不打算出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.13,0:14:46.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看我這樣  我還是很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.11,0:14:50.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  被爐取暖什麼的  忙死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:54.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那走吧  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:14:58.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也拜託千秋去買東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.37,0:14:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.08,0:15:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.41,0:15:07.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多積雪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.38,0:15:08.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.57,0:15:12.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬  幹嘛攢雪球
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.96,0:15:15.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然有雪  那當然是先打雪仗再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.73,0:15:17.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是骨子裡就喜歡胡鬧的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.69,0:15:19.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是要大家一起決定玩什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.75,0:15:21.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得我都做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.23,0:15:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看它這樣  它是個飯團哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.81,0:15:25.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.27,0:15:28.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃  扔掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.93,0:15:41.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  你們是要打雪仗嗎  打雪仗對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.06,0:15:44.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行啊  那就來戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.83,0:15:47.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我把你們都收拾掉  戰吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:50.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看我這樣  是很有力氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.04,0:15:52.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.15,0:15:55.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看我這樣  也看棒球比賽的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.29,0:15:58.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是壘球的扔法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.41,0:16:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看我這樣  也是喜歡足球的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.04,0:16:01.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:11.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們還真下手了啊  看我這次…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.00,0:16:13.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了哦  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.80,0:16:15.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次投犯規球哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.23,0:16:18.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小學生對中學生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.75,0:16:20.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  只有我是中學生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.14,0:16:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.77,0:16:23.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃我一球！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.78,0:16:24.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.47,0:16:30.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼只有我是這幅慘狀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.29,0:16:33.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是小學生對中學生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.78,0:16:34.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不公平吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.38,0:16:39.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且別看我這樣  其實都還沒有輸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:42.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快認輸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.54,0:16:43.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.76,0:16:46.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香也是來打雪仗的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.75,0:16:48.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘帶錢包了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.29,0:16:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有其他要買的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.60,0:16:53.19,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(540,300)\frz-27}鬼\N面\N具 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.60,0:16:53.19,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(800,360)\frz-27}節\N分\N的\N豆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:57.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然都走到這了  幹嘛不自己去買
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.83,0:17:00.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看我這樣  我還是很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.90,0:17:02.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.07,0:17:04.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是要回被爐裡去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:09.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐出去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:09.11,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}原句是節分撒豆子時說的「鬼は外」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.87,0:17:19.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.13,0:17:22.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼死了啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.87,0:17:37.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.77,0:17:42.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,節分？節分是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.22,0:17:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍不知道什麼是節分嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.33,0:17:48.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了  節分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.34,0:17:53.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡單的來說  就是在家裡撒豆子把惡鬼給趕出去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.95,0:17:55.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再把福請進來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.79,0:17:56.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯嘛  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.27,0:17:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道的很清楚嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.86,0:17:59.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.61,0:18:04.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的萬聖節也是  最近節日都好高雅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.72,0:18:06.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,節分從很久以前就有了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.11,0:18:09.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就由我來扮演鬼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.21,0:18:12.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  一邊說「鬼快出去」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.79,0:18:14.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊把這些豆撒在鬼身上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.33,0:18:16.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.71,0:18:21.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼快出去  鬼快出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.49,0:18:24.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.70,0:18:28.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要打敗我的話  就準備一億顆豆子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.32,0:18:29.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.23,0:18:33.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正常人家裡怎麼可能有一億顆豆子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.93,0:18:36.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼快出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.22,0:18:40.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是豆子也可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.87,0:18:41.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.80,0:18:42.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.52,0:18:43.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:46.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要丟熊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.82,0:18:48.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼快出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:50.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,福快來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.18,0:18:52.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.13,0:18:54.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿一億顆出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.38,0:18:57.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撒完了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.66,0:18:58.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撒完了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.19,0:19:00.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被撒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.27,0:19:02.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.39,0:19:07.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  不是說了撒豆子要適度嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.53,0:19:09.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.18,0:19:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收拾乾淨之後來吃點心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.17,0:19:13.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.95,0:19:24.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼也在收拾豆子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.97,0:19:29.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家特製  惠方蛋糕卷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.18,0:19:31.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  阿珍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:32.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.43,0:19:33.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.41,0:19:39.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,節分真是個好東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.77,0:19:42.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一塊不夠  再來一塊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.65,0:19:43.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:48.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說鬼可以隨便撒嬌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.65,0:19:52.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是鬼嘛  撒嬌有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.69,0:19:54.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  面具借我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.90,0:19:55.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.19,0:19:57.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請再給我一塊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.18,0:19:59.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  阿珍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:02.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋也再來一塊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.01,0:20:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.08,0:20:06.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是鬼也能拿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.13,0:20:10.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  那我去準備晚飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.84,0:20:19.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂鬼  你打算在家裡待到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.42,0:20:20.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.21,0:20:21.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼是要出去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.66,0:20:25.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難…難道說  身為鬼的我要被趕走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.91,0:20:29.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…能幫忙的鬼留下來倒也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.59,0:20:31.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然會幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.30,0:20:33.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那鬼  幫我續一杯咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.80,0:20:34.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.58,0:20:36.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.69,0:20:40.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂鬼  幫我揉揉肩膀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.90,0:20:42.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真會使喚鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:46.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂鬼  不想喝咖啡了幫我買瓶果汁回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.45,0:20:47.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是鬼吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.17,0:20:51.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不幹了！待遇太差幹不下去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.12,0:20:55.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍  鬼要是被小看了就玩完了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.17,0:20:56.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.61,0:21:00.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我來告訴你什麼是真正的鬼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.11,0:21:05.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂鬼  果汁還沒買來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.85,0:21:07.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己去買吧  蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.20,0:21:09.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那幫我揉肩膀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.61,0:21:11.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己揉去  蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.72,0:21:13.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那去打掃浴室
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.45,0:21:15.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天輪到你打掃吧  蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.64,0:21:17.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是鬼  
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.90,0:21:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是平時的千秋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.89,0:21:23.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  去給春香姐姐幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.62,0:21:27.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了那只是平時的千秋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.26,0:21:34.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  千秋  這個拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.94,0:21:36.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.00,0:21:41.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.52,0:21:46.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要放胡蘿蔔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.81,0:21:50.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.13,0:23:35.12,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(950,600)\fs45}秘密只在私底下說
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.15,0:23:24.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一話  秘密只在私底下說
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.76,0:23:26.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄告訴你  其實啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.72,0:23:29.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.15,0:23:31.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也不是什麼了不起的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.40,0:23:33.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦  千秋
